<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 03:13:55 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>特朗普风险推高美国收益率，美元飙升至38年高点附近</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-02/</link><description>由于投资者考虑唐纳德·特朗普连任总统的可能性，美国国债收益率飙升，周二美元兑日元徘徊在近38年高点附近。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 02:23:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>微软整合中国零售渠道</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/microsoft-consolidates-retail-channels-china-2024-07-02/</link><description>微软正在整合其在中国大陆的零售渠道，该公司在回应媒体报道称其将关闭其在全球第二大经济体的授权实体零售商网络时表示。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 01:52:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/microsoft-consolidates-retail-channels-china-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>美国国债收益率推高美元，日元贬值</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/us-yields-lift-dollar-leave-yen-languishing-2024-07-02/</link><description>美元受到美国国债收益率上升的支撑，周二人民币和日元等低收益货币也受到重创，日元汇率跌至1986年以来的最低水平。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 01:07:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/us-yields-lift-dollar-leave-yen-languishing-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国称美国瞄准人工智能无助于健康发展</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/china-says-us-targeting-ai-not-helpful-healthy-development-2024-07-01/</link><description>中国驻联合国特使周一表示，美国针对中国人工智能的某些投资无助于人工智能技术的“健康发展”，并且在全球治理方面将产生分歧。</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 21:58:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/china-says-us-targeting-ai-not-helpful-healthy-development-2024-07-01/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：美国收益率下跌，中国罕见惊喜</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-01/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 21:53:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-01/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉在第二季度交付报告发布前上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-rises-ahead-q2-deliveries-report-2024-07-01/</link><description>特斯拉股价周一上涨近 6%，此前一家重要的华尔街券商在特斯拉周二发布季度生产和交付报告之前将该股列入观察名单。</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 17:45:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-rises-ahead-q2-deliveries-report-2024-07-01/</guid></item><item><title>雷诺电动汽车部门 Ampere 与 LGES、CATL 合作开发电池技术</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/renaults-ev-unit-ampere-bet-lfp-technology-ev-batteries-2024-07-01/</link><description>雷诺旗下电动汽车部门 Ampere 周一表示，将在其电动汽车量产计划中纳入磷酸铁锂 (LFP) 技术，并与 LG Energy Solution (LGES) 和 CATL 合作，在欧洲建立供应链。</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 15:55:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/renaults-ev-unit-ampere-bet-lfp-technology-ev-batteries-2024-07-01/</guid></item><item><title>Chess-Ding vs Gukesh 世界冠军赛将在新加坡举行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/chess-ding-v-gukesh-world-championship-match-take-place-singapore-2024-07-01/</link><description>国际象棋联合会（FIDE）周一表示，印度古克什·D·D和卫冕冠军中国选手丁立人之间的经典国际象棋世界冠军赛将于11月20日至12月15日在新加坡举行。</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 12:39:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/chess-ding-v-gukesh-world-championship-match-take-place-singapore-2024-07-01/</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜将电视转播从中国转至俄罗斯卫星</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-switches-tv-transmission-russia-satellite-chinese-2024-07-01/</link><description>韩国统一部周一表示，朝鲜已将国家电视广播的传输从中国卫星改为俄罗斯卫星，这使得对此类广播的监控对韩国政府机构和媒体构成挑战。</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 09:12:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-switches-tv-transmission-russia-satellite-chinese-2024-07-01/</guid></item><item><title>中国向香港、澳门永久居民提供五年签证</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-offers-foreign-permanent-residents-hong-kong-macau-five-year-visas-2024-07-01/</link><description>中国国家移民管理局周一表示，前往中国大陆的香港和澳门永久居民的外国人可以申请有效期五年的多次入境旅游签证。</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 06:50:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-offers-foreign-permanent-residents-hong-kong-macau-five-year-visas-2024-07-01/</guid></item><item><title>中国少年选手张在印度尼西亚比赛中去世</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/chinese-junior-player-zhang-dies-during-event-indonesia-2024-07-01/</link><description>亚洲羽联和中国外交部周一对17岁的中国选手张志杰在印度尼西亚日惹举行的亚青赛期间倒在赛场上表示哀悼。</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 05:23:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/chinese-junior-player-zhang-dies-during-event-indonesia-2024-07-01/</guid></item><item><title>中国社交媒体公司谴责持刀袭击后针对日本人的仇恨言论</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-social-media-companies-condemn-hate-speech-against-japanese-after-knife-2024-07-01/</link><description>中国顶级社交媒体公司谴责了针对日本人的网络仇恨言论，并对上周造成一人死亡、一名日本母子受伤的持刀袭击事件引发的评论做出了强烈回应。</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 04:41:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-social-media-companies-condemn-hate-speech-against-japanese-after-knife-2024-07-01/</guid></item><item><title>波音公司重启向中国交付新飞机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/boeing-restarts-new-plane-deliveries-china-2024-07-01/</link><description>根据航班跟踪数据和两位消息人士的说法，波音公司已重新开始向中国交付宽体喷气式飞机，这些交付由于中国的监管审查而暂停，这也导致这家美国飞机制造商新的窄体飞机交付陷入停滞。</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 04:40:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/boeing-restarts-new-plane-deliveries-china-2024-07-01/</guid></item><item><title>采购经理人指数 (PMI) 显示，6 月份全球工厂活动表现不一</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-economy-asias-factory-activity-expands-june-solid-global-demand-2024-07-01/</link><description>调查显示，上个月欧洲制造业活动遭受重挫，但亚洲工厂势头强劲，政策制定者们希望该地区能够经受住中国需求疲软的打击。</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 02:55:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-economy-asias-factory-activity-expands-june-solid-global-demand-2024-07-01/</guid></item><item><title>在整体经济放缓的情况下，中国小企业的工厂活动有所增加</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-factory-activity-rises-fastest-pace-over-3-years-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-07-01/</link><description>一项私人指数显示，由于海外订单，中国小型制造商的工厂活动以 2021 年以来最快的速度增长，尽管更广泛的调查显示国内需求疲软和贸易摩擦导致工业部门再次收缩。</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 01:54:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-factory-activity-rises-fastest-pace-over-3-years-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-07-01/</guid></item></channel></rss>